-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 1.0

- Now supports sending multiple notifications for a single message by
  allowing multiple message ages to be specified with the "-t" option.

- Allow for some of the hard-coded paths to be modified.

- Fixed handling of sender addresses starting with a hyphen.

- Fixed treating missing info files as fatal errors.

- Allows for configuring the base qmail directory in $QMAILHOME.

- Switched to using bg-installer for installation.

- Updated for bglibs v2.

Development of this version has been sponsored by FutureQuest, Inc.
ossi@FutureQuest.net  http://www.FutureQuest.net/
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 0.93

- Added support for morercpthosts.cdb.

- Now defaults to not sending a copy of the nofication.

- Recoded to use iobuf libraries.

Development of this version has been sponsored by FutureQuest, Inc.
ossi@FutureQuest.net  http://www.FutureQuest.net/
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 0.92

- Added support for MIME-encoded attachments.

- Added support for loading an external bounce response message file.

Development of this version has been sponsored by FutureQuest, Inc.
ossi@FutureQuest.net  http://www.FutureQuest.net/
